title: The Not-So-Super Bowl | The Ringer NFL Show (Ep. 396)
description:
Bill Belichick and Tom Brady do it again, while Sean McVay and Jared Goff struggle every step of the way. What does this game tell us about the legacy of the Patriots and the future of the Rams?
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
